WEBVTT

02:19:06.316 --> 02:19:07.233
Anju, dear!

02:19:07.483 --> 02:19:08.483
Oh no!

02:19:08.983 --> 02:19:10.524
Dear! My child!

02:19:10.649 --> 02:19:12.899
Didn't I warn you
that Sahadevan isn't dependable?

02:19:14.066 --> 02:19:15.566
From what I know of him,

02:19:15.649 --> 02:19:18.483
he wouldn't hesitate to kill the boy
just to make the case stronger!
